[44155]={"[q3]Flying Machine","8 sec cast\nTools: Arclight Spanner , Blacksmith Hammer\nReagents:\nAdamantite Frame (2), Fel Iron Bar (30), Handful of Fel Iron Bolts (8), Star Wood (8), Adamantite Bar (5), Elemental Seaforium Charge (4)\n[q]An amazing machine that allows the Engineer to fly in Outland.\n[q3]Flying Machine Control\nBinds when used\nMount\n70\nRequiresEngineering\n(350)\n[q2]Use: Summons and dismisses a flying machine. This vehicle can only be used in Outland. (3 Sec Cooldown)\n[q]\"Requires expert riding skill or higher to use.\""},
[44157]={"[q4]Turbo-Charged Flying Machine","8 sec cast\nTools: Arclight Spanner , Blacksmith Hammer\nReagents:\nFlying Machine Control , Khorium Power Core (8), Felsteel Stabilizer (8), Hula Girl Doll\n[q]An amazing machine that allows the Engineer to fly in Outland. This one is turbo charged.\n[q4]Turbo-Charged Flying Machine Control\nBinds when used\nMount\n70\nRequiresEngineering\n(375)\n[q2]Use: Summons and dismisses a turbo-charged flying machine. This is a very fast ride. This vehicle can only be used in Outland. (3 Sec Cooldown)\n[q]\"Requires artisan riding skill or higher to use.\""},
